title: Friday Feb 12 2021 at 10am Special Atheist Question and Answer session at Bridges of Meaning
description:
You can find the Discord server here https://discord.gg/jdVk8XU

10am Friday Feb 12 at 10AM Pacific Standard Time.

It will be livestreamed but I only take questions from the BoM Discord Server.

Here it is https://youtu.be/aBXzNTIr0Vo
